# Tracked exceptions: canonical handoff manifests that downstream
# subprojects consume must be in git.
!subprojects/02_1_tokenizer_experiments/02_1_5_added_token_curation/manifests/*.jsonl
!subprojects/02_1_tokenizer_experiments/02_1_5_added_token_curation/manifests/*.json

# 02_1_7 intrinsic eval sweep — track decision artifacts + plots.
# Must un-ignore the artifacts dir explicitly (negation can't reach inside
# an ignored parent), then re-ignore the big regenerable bits inside it.
